OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775833867
OL,3,CUnion deal agreed to protect the
OL,4,Crights of Manchester Village Pride
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FManchester Village Pride has signed a
OL,8,Funion agreement which guarantees pay,
OL,9,Fhealth and safety standards and
OL,10,Fprotection against bullying and
OL,11,Fharassment for drag and burlesque
OL,12,Fperformers at the newly founded
OL,13,Ffestival.
OL,15,FThe agreement with the performers'
OL,16,Funion Equity was forged after the
OL,17,Fcollapse of Manchester Pride in 2025,
OL,18,Fwhich left dozens of performers unpaid
OL,19,Fand out of pocket by thousands of
OL,20,Fpounds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
