PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775833867
OL,3,CUnion deal agreed to protect the
OL,4,Crights of Manchester Village Pride
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FThe deal, endorsed unanimously by
OL,8,FEquity members, sets out minimum 20%
OL,9,Fdeposits, 30-day payment periods, and
OL,10,Fensures no performers will be asked to
OL,11,Fwork for free.
OL,13,FA series of health and safety
OL,14,Fprotections and a dignity at work
OL,15,Fpolicy are also included, protecting
OL,16,Fperformers from any bullying or
OL,17,Fharassment they might face in the line
OL,18,Fof work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
