PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775833867
OL,3,CUnion deal agreed to protect the
OL,4,Crights of Manchester Village Pride
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,FKaren Lockney, Equity's North West
OL,8,Fofficial, said: "We are delighted to
OL,9,Fsign this landmark union agreement
OL,10,Fwith Manchester Village Pride (MVP)."
OL,12,F"The work our members and the MVP
OL,13,Fboard of directors have done to reach
OL,14,Fthis agreement is the first of its
OL,15,Fkind, leading the way for other Prides
OL,16,Fto follow."
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
