OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775833867
OL,3,CUnion deal agreed to protect the
OL,4,Crights of Manchester Village Pride
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,F"This is at it should be ` a
OL,8,Fcelebration of LGBTQ+ rights must be
OL,9,Ftied to workers' rights, and this
OL,10,Fagreement protects performers' pay,
OL,11,Fterms and conditions and health and
OL,12,Fsafety."
OL,14,F"Manchester Village Pride is rooted in
OL,15,Fthe community it serves, and signing a
OL,16,Funion agreement helps rebuild
OL,17,Fperformers' trust after Manchester
OL,18,FPride went into liquidation last year."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
