OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775833867
OL,3,CUnion deal agreed to protect the
OL,4,Crights of Manchester Village Pride
OL,5,Cperformers
OL,7,F"Manchester has international
OL,8,Fsignificance for its championing of
OL,9,FLGBTQ+ rights and worker rights, so it
OL,10,Fis fitting this groundbreaking
OL,11,Fagreement ties these rights together."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@fO]
